summary: Rogue One modern AU : Captain of the Mexican NT!Cassian Andor and his unusually pessimistic droid friend!K2SO Cassian blinks up...
caption:
Rogue One modern AU : Captain of the Mexican NT!Cassian Andor and his unusually pessimistic droid friend!K2SO

Cassian blinks up at the droid; trust Kay to be least helpful when he actually needs him. 

He adjusts the band over his left arm and looks at his team who are waiting for his command. They’re not bad, by no means, but they weren’t great. And to beat the ruling champions they were going against ? The odds were definitely not in their favor. 

But he had to hope. The rebellious hearts were built on hope.

“Make ten men feel like a hundred.”

tags: I made a Vernal-as-Sabe edit forever ago happy to see that validated
summary: Also for my RWBY/Star Wars multifandom followers, in the V5 commentary Miles and Kerry actually made a joke about Vernal being...
body:
Also for my RWBY/Star Wars multifandom followers, in the V5 commentary Miles and Kerry actually made a joke about Vernal being Sabe.

After discussing the two uses of Raven’s mask (to hide the Spring Maiden eye flames and as a literal mask to help her project the image she wants to to people) they continued on completely deadpan to list two additional uses for it:

“One is that it exfoliates.”

“Yeah I mean you don’t keep looking that young without some sort of facial care.”

“Yeah it’s like a mud mask thing going on, and then the fourth and arguably most important, is that while there is Vernal, who acts as the Spring Maiden decoy, there’s also Natalie Portman, who acts as the Queen Amidala style decoy.”

“Yeah it’s so good to finally talk about that we’ve wanted to for years.”

“Yeah I mean, when George first approached us–[finally breaks composure and laughs]”
